      <div purpose="page-section">
        <div purpose="feature-with-image">
          <div purpose="feature-image">
            <img alt="Autonomous, with humans in the loop" src="/images/mdm-modern-change-management-600x435@2x.png">
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature-text">
            <h2>Every change reviewed and approved</h2>
            <p>Your security and compliance teams need to know that every change is reviewed, approved, and reversible. Fleet makes that easy without slowing you down.</p>
            <div purpose="section-buttons">
              <a purpose="section-button" href="/ai">More on AI-powered IT</a>
              <animated-arrow-button href="/infrastructure-as-code">Manage devices as code</animated-arrow-button>
