                Approval before deployment
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div purpose="feature-text">
              <p>
                Every change goes through a pull request. Review and approve from Slack or the Fleet UI. Nothing ships without sign-off.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature-item">
            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="Full audit trail" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-audit-trail-20x20@2x.png">
