                Full audit trail
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div purpose="feature-text">
              <p>
                Every change is tracked — who proposed it, who approved it, when it shipped. Your security team gets the logs they need without you assembling them.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature-item">
            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="Instant rollback" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-rollback-20x20@2x.png">
