                Instant rollback
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div purpose="feature-text">
              <p>
                Roll back any change with a single revert. Changes become less risky, not more work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature-item">
            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="AI-assisted policies" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-ai-assisted-polices-20x20@2x.png">
              <h5>
                AI-assisted policies
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div purpose="feature-text">
              <p>
                Describe what you want in plain language. Fleet drafts the policy. A human reviews and approves before anything reaches a device.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
